2. Write a program using functions to print the following pattern  
    *
    **
    ***
    ****

Code : 

public class practice{
    static void stars(int n){
        for(int i=1 ; i<=n ; i++){
            for (int j=1 ; j<=i ; j++){
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.print("\n");
        }
    }
    public static void main(String[] args){
        stars(4);
    }
}

