4. Write a function to print the following pattern
    ****
    ***
    **
    *

Code :

public class practice {
    static void printPattern(int n) {
        for(int i = n; i >= 1; i--) {
            for(int j = 1; j <= i; j++) {
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        printPattern(4);
    }
}

